mpirical analysis of a quasi experiment at the stanford law school 2000 2007 2009 04 01 measuring explicit political positions of media 2008 10 29 improving the presentation and interpretation of online ratings data with model based figures 2008 07 01 author daniel e ho stanford law school dho law stanford edu 650 723.9560 cloudy 51 f 2012 stanford university system requirements help virtual tour
